nodes.text: Victor Botha (born May 22, 1982) is a South African actor who portrayed a death trooper in the Rogue One: A Star Wars Story.

Victor Botha was born in the Free State South Africa. He previously was a soldier in the British Army serving in Afghanistan and Iraq. Victor has a lot of military experience especially with firearms. He enjoys sport especially rugby, cricket and F1 and lives in the United Kingdom with his wife and son.
